            "<p><strong>Implementation Note:</strong> Creating the rep-tiles takes time for students to cut, manipulate and draw. Due to this it may take 1.5 days to complete this task. Having a conversation after students have completed the Initial Challenge can help them focus their thinking between the two class periods. </p>"
